Privacy Policy
The TDL Group Corp. (“TDL”), the proud owner of the TIM HORTONS® restaurant brand, knows that your privacy is important. This Privacy Policy sets out our privacy practices that apply when you visit TIM HORTONS® restaurants that we own and operate or use any TIM HORTONS® branded website, mobile or tablet application (“App”), digital in-restaurant kiosk, or other TIM HORTONS® online service or platform, as well as our other interactions with you, including on third-party platforms (such as social media).
